&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Technical Project Manager at Hellbender, you will be responsible for planning and&amp;nbsp;executing multiple concurrent projects and for providing the technical guidance needed to&amp;nbsp;transition projects from conception, through design, and into production. You will be the main&amp;nbsp;customer facing contact and directly responsible for the budget, performance, and schedule of&amp;nbsp;assigned projects. This role requires technical expertise, attention to detail, as well as the ability&amp;nbsp;to collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams. The ideal candidate will have a solid&amp;nbsp;background in electromechanical systems and experience leading technical teams through&amp;nbsp;complex engineering projects. United States veteran and diverse candidates are encouraged to&amp;nbsp;apply at any experience level.&lt;/p&gt;
